OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fcloudy and wet evening with some
OL,7,Ffairly persistent rain arriving, this
OL,8,Flocally heavy at times. Staying rather
OL,9,Fwet overnight but the rain turning
OL,10,Fsomewhat lighter and more patchy
OL,11,Flater. Another mild and frost free
OL,12,Fnight.
OL,13,
OL,14,CFriday:FCloudy and often damp during
OL,15,Fthe morning with spells of light rain
OL,16,Fand drizzle. Brighter breaks may occur
OL,17,Fbut heavy showers or longer periods of
OL,18,Frain probably developing later. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
