OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,6,FOvernight rain clearing to lengthy
OL,7,Fsunny periods on Saturday with
OL,8,Fisolated showers. Turning damp and
OL,9,Fwindy on Sunday. A chance of showery
OL,10,Frain arriving on Monday. Staying mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
